data.title: Coins of Bohemia
data.meta_description: Coins of Bohemia - Free download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. The document provides biographies of early Dukes of Bohemia, including Borivoj I (851-888), Spytihnev I (c. 894-915), Vratislaus I (c. 888-921), Wenceslaus I (c. 907-935), and Boleslav I (the Cruel) (c. 935-c. 972). It discusses their reigns and key events, such as Borivoj declaring himself the first Duke of Bohemia, Wenceslaus' Christianization of Bohemia, and Boleslav gaining the throne through murdering his brother Wenceslaus.
